author: uschindler
msg: Fix a small problem where the "svnversion" command may output an error message and therefore creates invalid manifest (with special chars included). This checks with regex, if the returned SVN revision is according to spec, otherwise it writes "unknown" to manifest

author: desruisseaux
msg: WKT: document relationship between AbstractIdentifiedObject.isHeuristicMatchForName(String) and section B.5.2 of OGC-12-063r5.
